        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "CHAPTER four.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1495_138027_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1495/138027/1495_138027_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "\"That is not where the mistake is,\" replied Samson; \"it is, that before the ass has turned up, the author speaks of Sancho as being mounted on it.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1495_138027_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1495/138027/1495_138027_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "\"I don't know what to say to that,\" said Sancho, \"unless that the historian made a mistake, or perhaps it might be a blunder of the printer's.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1495_138027_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1495/138027/1495_138027_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "\"No doubt that's it,\" said Samson; \"but what became of the hundred crowns?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1495_138027_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1495/138027/1495_138027_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "Did they vanish?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1495_138027_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1495/138027/1495_138027_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "Let each look to himself and not try to make out white black, and black white; for each of us is as God made him, aye, and often worse.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1495_138027_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1495/138027/1495_138027_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "\"I will take care,\" said Carrasco, \"to impress upon the author of the history that, if he prints it again, he must not forget what worthy Sancho has said, for it will raise it a good span higher.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1495_138027_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1495/138027/1495_138027_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "Whereat Sancho observed, \"The author looks for money and profit, does he? It will be a wonder if he succeeds, for it will be only hurry, hurry, with him, like the tailor on Easter Eve; and works done in a hurry are never finished as perfectly as they ought to be.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1495_138027_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1495/138027/1495_138027_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "Let master Moor, or whatever he is, pay attention to what he is doing, and I and my master will give him as much grouting ready to his hand, in the way of adventures and accidents of all sorts, as would make up not only one second part, but a hundred.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1495_138027_000016_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1495/138027/1495_138027_000016_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "The good man fancies, no doubt, that we are fast asleep in the straw here, but let him hold up our feet to be shod and he will see which foot it is we go lame on.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1495_138027_000017_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1495/138027/1495_138027_000017_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "He commended his very praiseworthy and gallant resolution, but admonished him to proceed with greater caution in encountering dangers, because his life did not belong to him, but to all those who had need of him to protect and aid them in their misfortunes.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1495_138027_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1495/138027/1495_138027_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "\"There's where it is, what I abominate, Senor Samson,\" said Sancho here; \"my master will attack a hundred armed men as a greedy boy would half a dozen melons.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1495_138027_000018_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1495/138027/1495_138027_000018_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "Body of the world, senor bachelor!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1495_138027_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1495/138027/1495_138027_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "\"Brother Sancho,\" said Carrasco, \"you have spoken like a professor; but, for all that, put your trust in God and in Senor Don Quixote, for he will give you a kingdom, not to say an island.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1495_138027_000022_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1495/138027/1495_138027_000022_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "Nay, only look at my disposition, is that likely to show ingratitude to anyone?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1495_138027_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1495/138027/1495_138027_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "\"God grant it,\" said Don Quixote; \"we shall see when the government comes; and I seem to see it already.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1495_138027_000026_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1495/138027/1495_138027_000026_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "Carrasco promised all, and then took his leave, charging Don Quixote to inform him of his good or evil fortunes whenever he had an opportunity; and thus they bade each other farewell, and Sancho went away to make the necessary preparations for their expedition.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1495_138027_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1495/138027/1495_138027_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "CHAPTER five",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1495_138027_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1495/138027/1495_138027_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "OF THE SHREWD AND DROLL CONVERSATION THAT PASSED BETWEEN SANCHO PANZA AND HIS WIFE TERESA PANZA, AND OTHER MATTERS WORTHY OF BEING DULY RECORDED",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1495_138027_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1495/138027/1495_138027_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "Sancho came home in such glee and spirits that his wife noticed his happiness a bowshot off, so much so that it made her ask him, \"What have you got, Sancho friend, that you are so glad?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1495_138027_000031_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1495/138027/1495_138027_000031_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "To which he replied, \"Wife, if it were God's will, I should be very glad not to be so well pleased as I show myself.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1495_138027_000032_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1495/138027/1495_138027_000032_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "\"I don't understand you, husband,\" said she, \"and I don't know what you mean by saying you would be glad, if it were God's will, not to be well pleased; for, fool as I am, I don't know how one can find pleasure in not having it.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1495_138027_000037_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1495/138027/1495_138027_000037_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "\"I can tell you, wife,\" said Sancho, \"if I did not expect to see myself governor of an island before long, I would drop down dead on the spot.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1495_138027_000038_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1495/138027/1495_138027_000038_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "How many there are in the world who live without a government, and continue to live all the same, and are reckoned in the number of the people.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1495_138027_000038_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1495/138027/1495_138027_000038_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "The best sauce in the world is hunger, and as the poor are never without that, they always eat with a relish.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1495_138027_000038_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1495/138027/1495_138027_000038_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "But mind, Sancho, if by good luck you should find yourself with some government, don't forget me and your children.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1495_138027_000041_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1495/138027/1495_138027_000041_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "\"Tut, you fool,\" said Sancho; \"it will be only to practise it for two or three years; and then dignity and decorum will fit her as easily as a glove; and if not, what matter?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1495_138027_000044_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1495/138027/1495_138027_000044_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "It is this sort of talk, and what Sancho says lower down, that made the translator of the history say he considered this chapter apocryphal.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1495_138027_000045_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1495/138027/1495_138027_000045_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "No, stay as you are, growing neither greater nor less, like a tapestry figure-Let us say no more about it, for Sanchica shall be a countess, say what you will.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1495_138027_000046_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1495/138027/1495_138027_000046_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "I was always a lover of equality, brother, and I can't bear to see people give themselves airs without any right.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1495_138027_000047_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1495/138027/1495_138027_000047_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "What have Cascajo, and the broaches and the proverbs and the airs, to do with what I say?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1495_138027_000053_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1495/138027/1495_138027_000053_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1495",
        "content": "\"Resolved, you should say, woman,\" said Sancho, \"not revolved.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    }
]